fr.lirmm.graphik.graal.api.core

Interface AtomSet

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CloseableIterable<Atom>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    InMemoryAtomSet, RdbmsStore, Store, TripleStore
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractAtomSet, AbstractImmutableAtomSet, AbstractInMemoryAtomSet, AbstractRdbmsStore, AbstractStore, AbstractTripleStore, AdHocRdbmsStore, DefaultInMemoryGraphStore, GraphDBStore, LinkedListAtomSet, MappedStore, NaturalRDBMSStore, Neo4jStore, RDF4jStore

    public interface AtomSet
extends CloseableIterable<Atom>
    This interface represents a set of atoms. You can interpret this set like you want, disjunction or conjunction of atoms. However, in Graal, it is almost always interpreted as a conjunction.
    Author:
    Cl√©ment Sipieter (INRIA)
